node.text: NordicTrack Care 3-Year Annual Maintenance Plan for Fitness Equipment $0 to $999.99
NordicTrack T5, Connect with your own device, SmartAdjust, Active Pulse, Body, Heart and Mind
The more you workout with iFIT, the smarter it gets with SmartAdjust technology
NordicTrack T5 comes with adjustable cushioning, device shelf and is compact to fit in your space
Personalized workouts, real-time workouts stats, sync all your fitness data in one place

Results require consistency and effective workouts. Thats what the NordicTrack T Series 5 Treadmill and iFIT Train Membership (sold separately) get you. Together, they create a workout experience unlike any other that keeps you coming back for more. NordicTracks powerful machine, paired with iFITs workouts and technology, puts results within anyones reach. About the T Series 5 Treadmill: Sign into your iFIT account on your own device and connect it to the T Series 5 Treadmill. Your home page will show the next workout in your personalized plan. As you work out, iFIT tracks your performance and automatically changes the treadmills 0-10% incline range, and 0-10 MPH to exactly what you need, so every workout is hands-free and personalized to you. Add your own Bluetooth-enabled heart rate monitor, and iFIT can automatically change your workout intensity to keep you in a target zone with ActivePulse. The KeyFlex cushioned deck is designed to provide support to absorb impact and make walking and running more comfortable. The device shelf keeps your phone or tablet in an optimal viewing position. This treadmill is compact and designed to fit most living spaces. About iFIT: iFIT Trainers are professional athletes, fitness experts, and more. They know how to help you get lasting results. iFIT features over 10,000 workouts and is the worlds largest outdoor workout library. iFIT Trainers will help you with form, keep you motivated to finish strong, and offer insights about global locations so you stay engaged in short and long workouts.

[Powered by iFIT] - Get more out of NordicTrack with iFIT Get coaching by expert iFIT Trainers in workouts that adapt to your fitness level and goals with our SmartAdjust technology (iFIT subscription required)

[ActivePulse] - Heart-rate-zone training is effective and iFIT makes it easier than ever. With a heart rate monitor, ActivePulse automatically adjusts the speed and incline to keep you in the targeted zone (subscription required)
[SmartAdjust] - Your treadmill automatically follows your iFIT Trainers speed and terrain, and adapts to your fitness level (subscription required)
[AI Coach (coming soon)] - iFIT AI Coach will help you set a goal, then automatically schedule the right workouts for you (subscription required)

[0-10 MPH] - 0-10 MPH means you can run up to a 6-minute mile pace right on your treadmill. Pick the speed that feels best, or iFIT can control your speed automatically for a hands-free, immersive experience (subscription required)
[KeyFlex Cushioning] - KeyFlex cushioning provides enough support to absorb impact so that walking and running is more comfortable. Ease your body into regular movement

[10% Incline] - 0-10% incline range supports your goals and training plans. Train for a 5K, marathon, long hikes, and more. The large incline range helps you target more muscle groups to train your body for more
[Speed & Incline Buttons] - Quickly change the speed or incline to the intensity of choice with a single button press

[5" LCD Display & Device Shelf] - See your live workout stats on the clear LCD display. Or, connect your own device to iFIT and rest it on the device shelf to follow iFIT Trainers in workouts around the world (subscription required)
[3rd Party Apps] - iFIT syncs with Strava, Garmin, Google Fit, and Apple Health, so you can store all of your data in one place (subscription required)
